r1623 | fishbait | 2007-09-23 23:38:14 +1000 (Sun, 23 Sep 2007) | 1 line

?\194?\171 gmTicket command moved to c flags instead of g. Giving an account a c flag will allow the account to access gmTickets and the ability to join the sync channel. This fixes the problem where previously giving an account the g flag would let the account use the command, but would not be allowed to join the channel.
