sb@il patch for aurastate flags in PVP
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1542 | Zack | 2007-09-18 02:40:13 +1000 (Tue, 18 Sep 2007) | 5 lines

do not use this revision yet (99% there are problems with it). Just updating to take it to another pc. NTY
The idea is to make monsters like onixia move faster then a turtle crawl.
you will need to alter your tables later with something like this : 
ALTER TABLE creature_proto ADD walk_speed FLOAT DEFAULT "2.5" NOT NULL AFTER death_state;
ALTER TABLE creature_proto ADD run_speed FLOAT DEFAULT "8" NOT NULL AFTER walk_speed;
------------------------------------------------------------------------
