r1196 | LordDraike | 2007-08-23 18:22:56 +1000 (Thu, 23 Aug 2007) | 4 lines

- Disabled IF_BREAD_SELLER.gm. 
. To re-enable, just uncomment the line I removed.

. Why was this disabled? It'd require you have certain waypoints in creature_waypoints table. To maintain consistency to IF_MEAT_VENDOR.gm and other tables, we should try to make them not require dependencies like this and add WPs in the script itself.
