r1072 | burlex | 2007-08-14 12:46:27 +1000 (Tue, 14 Aug 2007) | 1 line

ppc work
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1071 | Burlex | 2007-08-14 12:33:41 +1000 (Tue, 14 Aug 2007) | 7 lines

* Implemented loot chances for heroic mode, as well as minimum and maximum count (for lemon:P)
. SQL Changes:
alter table creatureloot add column percentchance float(0) default 0;
alter table creatureloot add column mincount int(30) default 1;
alter table creatureloot add column maxcount int(30) default 1;

repeat for each loot table, replacing creatreloot with appropriate table name.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
