r896 | Burlex | 2007-07-17 11:09:43 +1000 (Tue, 17 Jul 2007) | 9 lines

* Fixed VC7 release compile.
* Fixed VC8 compiles. Also cleaned up un-needed configurations.
* Moved worldmap_info to storage system, can be reloaded now.
- Added required quest, and required item to worldmap_info for attunements.
SQL Query to update is:

alter table worldmap_info add column required_quest int(30) not null default 0 after lvl_mod_a;
and
alter table worldmap_info add column required_itemid int(30) not null default 0 after lvl_mod_a;
