r502 | Burlex | 2007-06-24 23:43:11 +1000 (Sun, 24 Jun 2007) | 1 line

+ Added Player::m_lastSpeed floats. These store the last speeds sent to the client, avoiding the need to send UpdateSpeed packets all the time. This will both reduce bandwidth usage of the server a lot, as well as fix the client temporary freezeups in populated areas.
