------------------------------------------------------------------------
r64 | sinistry | 2007-05-26 05:07:07 +1000 (Sat, 26 May 2007) | 13 lines

-fixed a crash at shutdown when a thread related to console was running while being deleted.
-fixed a crash due to a bad for loop while thread was being shutdown.
-fixed a issue where units couldnt cast spells due to player attacks. Units will now avoid casting time delay.
-fixed a bug where u couldnt enter a heroic instance propely or couldnt leave one.
-added Heroic support to instances.
--Npcs will gain 1.5x more hp, damage and health and also increase in level depending on worldmap_info lvl_mod_a column.
--Added Heroic lockout to instance save manager. default lockout is 15 hours.
-fixed a bug where you could duplicate charters and when deleting one would bug the other after a relog.
-added thread locking to all instance save manager classes.
-fixed a bug that didnt allow players to join proper saved instance after a server restart due to a bad guid.
-instance difficulty now gets saved.

update worldmapinfo, instances and characters.
